Package: seuratBubblePlot
Type: Package
Title: Create bubble plot of scRNAseq expression data from Seurat
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R: person("Miles", "Smith", email = "miles-smith@omrf.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: Creates a bubble plot displaying scRNAseq expression data where the size of bubbles indicates the percentage of a cell popluation expressing a gene and the color intensity indicates normalized expression levels.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0),
  plyr,
  dplyr,
  glue,
  HGNChelper,
  magrittr,
  Seurat,
  tidyr,
  tibble,
  compositions,
  ggplot2,
  grDevices,
  viridis,
  RColorBrewer,
  org.Hs.eg.db,
  gtools
